    "nom_orig": "Miss[SP]Kaori",
    "texte_orig": "A[SP]woman[SP]who[SP]came[SP]here[SP]said[SP]this:[SP][1432][NULL][NULL][0014]I[SP]want[SP]to[SP]be\nan[SP]adult[SP]who[SP]can[SP]still[SP]trust[SP]in[SP]youth...[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]\nWell[SP]then,[SP]may[SP]your[SP]day[SP]be[SP]a[SP]wonderful[SP]one.",
