    "texte_orig": "Is[SP]there[SP]anything[SP]else[SP]I[SP]can[SP]help[SP]you[SP]with?\n[U+1208][U+0004]Heal\nTalk[SP]to[SP]Miss[SP]Kaori\nNever[SP]mind\nLeave\n[U+1109][E2][E3][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Miss[SP]Kaori\nAnd[SP]what[SP]do[SP]you[SP]propose[SP]we[SP]speak[SP]of?\n[U+1208][0002]Make[SP]small[SP]talk\nAsk[SP]about[SP]healing\n[U+1109][E2][E3][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Miss[SP]Kaori\nPardon[SP]me,[SP]but[SP]it[SP]seems[SP]you[SP]don't[SP]have[SP]enough\nmoney.[SP]Please[SP]come[SP]again.",
