    "offset": 362494,
    "slot_size": 328,
    "data_size": 324,
    "nom_orig": "Older[SP]woman",
    "texte_orig": "[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]The[SP]lion's[SP]roar[SP]echoes[SP]far[SP]and[SP]wide...[1432][NULL][NULL][0014][1205][U+000F][SP]Is[SP]that\nhow[SP]it[SP]went?[1205][U+000F][SP]Some[SP]say[SP]that[SP]passage[SP]is[SP]about\nthe[SP]Leonids...[1205][U+000F][SP]Will[SP]it[SP]come[SP]true[SP]too...?",
