  {
    "id": 62,
    "offset": 364322,
    "slot_size": 296,
    "data_size": 292,
    "nom_orig": "Concerned[SP]mother",
    "texte_orig": "That's[SP]why[SP]cults[SP]like[SP]that[SP]are[SP]so[SP]scary.[SP]Who\nknows[SP]what[SP]they'll[SP]believe[SP]or[SP]do?[SP]Hm?[SP]Me?\nOf[SP]course[SP]I[SP]don't[SP]believe[SP]such[SP]tripe.",
