    "texte_orig": "I[SP]can't[SP]believe[SP]those[SP]soldiers[SP]have[SP]invaded...\nWas[SP]that[SP]book[SP]true[SP]after[SP]all?[SP]Um...[SP]I[SP]had[SP]a\nfeeling[SP]it[SP]would[SP]be[SP]from[SP]the[SP]start!",
